## Verification Plan

### Automated
- Server starts without errors
- `POST /register` returns pendingUserId (does NOT create User)
- `POST /verify-otp` with correct OTP creates User + returns token
- `POST /verify-otp` with wrong OTP returns error
- `POST /login` with unverified email returns appropriate error
- Google OAuth still works with role selection

### Manual
- Test full registration flow in browser
- Verify OTP email arrives
- Verify Google sign-up with role selection
